### Manual Verification Path
- Admins can trigger a re-sync via:
  ```bash
  curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/crm-resync \
    -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
    -d '{"userId": "USER_ID_HERE"}'
  ```
- Alerts will be sent to the email defined in `ADMIN_ALERT_EMAIL` or `ops@nextacademyedu.com`.
